text = "TODO:
- Figure out Possession Potion Recipes.
- Add one-time weak possession potion status effect.
- Set up the recipe book contents.
- Add plants in appropriate places.
- Determine which alternate solutions are acceptable, if any.
- Determine if necessary to prevent any soft-locks or just require a reset.

New:
Possession Potion

Step 1:
- Use given possession potion to get possession postion recipe.
*NOTE: May be difficult to limit possession to one use. May need to make a new status effect entirely that limits to one possession.
- Use crafted possession potion to get speed potion recipe.
- Use possession potion to get third person to craft speed potion and use it to access the area with the button used to open the exit path.
- You CAN skip the steps to get the recipes if you already know the recipes and that is fine."
